{"tid":1424751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警無委任証 我真係好擔心有平民去冒警 點算好好驚呀我","createTime":"2019-08-06T16:28:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T16:40:26.000Z","uid":220864,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"27b607a60434aa3c9f9c453bafa393c11a4ac677","tid":1424751,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:28:21.000Z","msg":"突然諗到<br />\n以子之矛攻子之盾<br />\n我地一直都懷疑無委任証嘅黑警冒警<br />\n咁個問題係一直都處於<span style=\"color: red;\">懷疑</span><br />\n<br />\n利申我真係<span style=\"color: red;\">唔建議</span>任何人做犯法野<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但係我真係好擔心<br />\n會有4至5個一組嘅人<br />\n著哂黑色衫隨街問人攞身份證查<br />\n姐係d白衫黑社會個d<br />\n或者犯罪份子<br />\n會透過黑警而家呢個漏洞<br />\n去隨街攞人d個人資料<br />\n如果d人再仔細d<br />\n求其攞個卡套出嚟就話自己係黑警<br />\n要求人地攞身份證出嚟同搜人個袋<br />\n咁真係人心惶惶囉</span><br />\n我係表達緊我的擔憂<br />\n<br />\n大家真係唔好咁做<br />\n如果唔係以後班狗都要攞委任証出嚟先做得野架啦<br />\n同埋冒警真係犯法架<br />\n<br />\n當懷疑變成事實<br />\n咁一切的懷疑都係合理的<br />\n<br />\n真係唔好做犯法野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cd6ea7716fb06aab2dee14b129c04b09de972a2","tid":1424751,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:29:02.000Z","msg":"唔好失民心呀<br />\n但係我好擔心黑社會同犯罪分子會透過呢個漏洞<br />\n攞人身份證去銀行借錢呀"},{"pid":"5097eee5bb1e4b05328b26852147333432cc19b8","tid":1424751,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:29:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c58d4145246cf1073fc59647ff2ecc786975cc24","tid":1424751,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:29:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a7a6e9bd394d2bd667b211e74a60f648d63662","tid":1424751,"uid":220864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm